text: Héctor Elizondo Nájera (born 7 August 1925) is a Mexican former sport shooter. He competed in the 25 metre rapid fire pistol event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. He is the older brother of Jesús Elizondo. ==References== Category:1925 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Mexican male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Mexico Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Tampico, Tamaulipas
